This is my first work in Hammer.

Well, this is basically the popular map awp_lego by mck-76 with a bombsite in the center of map.
I thought it would be a nice addition, because de_awp maps are quite fun.

Please feedback saying what you think of the addition, how this changed the gameplay, etc..
